headline: Why Rivian (RIVN) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of electric vehicle manufacturer Rivian (NASDAQ:RIVN) jumped 3.3% in the morning session after reports showed the electric vehicle maker's U.S. sales hit a 10-month high in July. The company recorded over 4,200 vehicles sold, which marked a 20% jump from June.
